        <div class="info-panel" id="infoPanel">
            <h3>Click on any section to learn more!</h3>
            <p>Each section of the wheel represents a different type of intelligence according to Howard Gardner's theory of multiple intelligences. Click on any colored section to discover more about that specific intelligence type.</p>
        </div>
